You skin the dead rabbit with the dagger.
> eat dead rabbit

> eat dead rabbit
You and Much share the raw rabbit for the next few days. It's chewy but it has stopped you from starving to death. A day later the cell door unlocks and two guards push two new inmates into the cell with you.
> speak to will scarlet

> speak to will scarlet
'Cousin, what brings you to these lavish surroundings?' you enquire.

'Robin, it seems Gisbourne caught us both 'borrowing' food in Nottingham market and we both had different ideas on punishment. I preferred his head on a lance and he wanted my head on the chopping block.' smiles Will.

'Any plans for an escape?' you ask.

'Well I did perchance relieve one of the guards with a certain key to this cell.' Will grins and hands you an iron key.

'Time to leave the Sheriff's hospitality.' you smile.
